<item>
            <title>[LU-17963] sometime touch command cannot change mtime</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17963</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;First create a file, then change its mtime immediately (touch command, or utimes/utimensat system call). Sometime mtime is not changed.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The bug can be reproduced in sanity/39_d easily in the development of nanosecond timestamps, but rarely/never be reproduced in current version with second granularity timestamps.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="82977">LU-17963</key>
            <summary>sometime touch command cannot change mtime</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11303&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
